  "body": "\r\n### Description\r\nAs a user I would lie to be able to access teku version information via prometheus.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nA metric in prometheus that provides the version, for example:\r\n\r\n```\r\nteku_info{version=\"21.2.0\"} 1\r\n```\r\n\r\nwould be nice. Additional labels can be added for other items if desired (commit hash or whatever).",
