    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Is this label names or label values where the restrictions apply?  As far as I can see label values have no restrictions, so a metric\r\n\r\n```\r\nteku_info{version=\"v21.2.0+42-gb443919\"} 1\r\n```\r\n\r\nwould be acceptable, although that's somewhat verbose compared to other implementations and so\r\n\r\n```\r\nteku_info{version=\"21.2.0\" release=\"v21.2.0+42-gb443919\"} 1\r\n```\r\n\r\nmay make more sense, with `release` having the full details and 'version' being the headline value used elsewhere in your release notes _etc_.",
